  "texts": [
    "It addresses uncertainties from both LiDAR measurement noise and pose estimation error through probabilistic plane representation.Instead of the variants of the ICP algorithm, the NDT algorithm can be employed, even when using features.",
    "NDT-LOAM [22] initially obtains approximate odometry using the weighted NDT (wNDT) algorithm.",
    "This initial estimate is then refined by incorporating corner and surface features.",
    "E-LOAM [45] extracts geometric and intensity features, enhances these features with local structural information, and estimates odometry with D2D-NDT matching.",
    "Wang et al. [141] propose a coarse-to-fine registration metric with NDT and PLICP (point-to-line ICP) [17]."
  ],
